Bandar Udara Internasional Sky Harbor Phoenix

Bandara Internasional Phoenix Sky Harbor adalah bandara internasional Phoenix, Amerika Serikat dengan kode IATA PHX.

Please Note: Passenger totals for the domestic flights are based on a 12 month scale ending April, 2012.

Sky Harbor has an average of 1,232 aircraft operations per day.
There are 75 aircraft based at Sky Harbor.
